OL,3,CTeam Reform smashes Plymouth's
OL,4,Cpolitical duopoly on dramatic election
OL,5,Cnight
OL,7,FElection nights are so often about
OL,8,Fimages. How things look is almost as
OL,9,Fimportant as the policy detail
OL,10,Funderneath.
OL,12,FThe picture which will stick in my
OL,13,Fmind from the extraordinary 2026 local
OL,14,Felection count in Plymouth is of a
OL,15,FReform UK supporter sporting a
OL,16,Fturquoise football shirt, complete
OL,17,Fwith 'Farage 10' emblazoned on the
OL,18,Fback, loudly leading the celebrations
OL,19,Fas the city's political landscape was
OL,20,Fturned on its head.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/6
