FL,437,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43606
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F436A1778415071
OL,3,CTeam Reform smashes Plymouth's
OL,4,Cpolitical duopoly on dramatic election
OL,5,Cnight
OL,7,FAs the clock ticked towards 4am on
OL,8,FFriday morning, I asked him what his
OL,9,Fbiggest challenge would be. He smiled
OL,10,Fand said simply: 'People management'.
OL,12,FMost of Plymouth's 14 new Reform
OL,13,Fcouncillors are entering political
OL,14,Flife for the first time. After decades
OL,15,Fof a two-party system, the underdogs
OL,16,Fhave finally been promoted to the big
OL,17,Fleague.
OL,19,FGetting to the top is one thing. The
OL,20,Fquestion now is whether they can stay
OL,21,Fthere.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/6
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
